head-chappell@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amazons-radiohead-chappell@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amazons-radiohead-chappell@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amazons-radiohead-chappell@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/amazons-radiohead-chappell@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-amazons">亚马逊人</a>在他们称之为“我的扭结”的歌曲中分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/radiohead">广播电台（Radiohead）</a>的混搭。在下面查看。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-amazons-interview-pitch-black-21st-century-fiction-royal-blood-politics-masculinity-3809874">他们的新专辑中的亚马逊以及为什么“小说”可能是“ 21世纪的定义词之一”</a></strong></li></ul><p>该录音是在本周早些时候在BBC Radio 1举行的一次非常特别的Maida Vale会议上完成的，并且预计他们即将发行的第四张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-amazons-announce-intimate-december-2024-21st-century-prologue-tour-dates-buy-tickets-3810543">“ 21世纪小说”。</a></p><p>在曲目中，乐队将Chappell Roan曲目“ My Kink Is Karma”与经典的Radiohead Hit命中“ Creep”融合在一起，并将自己的旋转放在这两个上。</p><p>随着混搭，乐队捕捉到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover/chappell-roan-05-02-2024-3582467">前<em>NME</em> Cover Star</a>的单曲的同样的情感和通风 - 这是她大型首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/chappell-roan-the-rise-and-fall-of-a-midwest-princess-review-debut-album-radar-3499595">《中西部公主的兴起和堕落》</a>中的第二首曲目。他们还捕捉到与1992年摇滚经典赛中所见的内省和忧郁感。</p><p>他们作为BBC Sounds的一部分分享了Radio 1的完整会议，Maida Vale的露面也看到他们表演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-amazons-team-up-with-royal-blood-for-raucous-new-single-my-blood-3827652">皇家血液协作曲目“ My Blood”</a>的表演，以及他们的热门歌曲“ Love Is Love Is to Dog来自地狱”。</p><p>在下面查看Chappell Roan和Radiohead Mash-up的片段，或<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/sounds/play/m0028gds" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>收听BBC的